{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":992,"text":"Ichthyology,"},{"time":2628,"text":"the study of fishes."},{"time":4112,"text":"It looks like a big, boring word,"},{"time":6994,"text":"but it's actually quite exciting,"},{"time":9199,"text":"because ichthyology is the only \"ology\""},{"time":12196,"text":"with \"YOLO\" in it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":13551,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":15359,"text":"Now, to the cool kids in the audience,"},{"time":17209,"text":"you already know, YOLO stands for\n\"you only live once,\""},{"time":21410,"text":"and because I only have one life,"},{"time":23096,"text":"I'm going to spend it doing\nwhat I always dreamt of doing:"},{"time":25883,"text":"seeing the hidden wonders of the world\nand discovering new species."},{"time":29068,"text":"And that's what I get to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30873,"text":"Now, in recent years, I really focused\non caves for finding new species."},{"time":35352,"text":"And it turns out, there's lots of new\ncavefish species out there."},{"time":38642,"text":"You just have to know where to look,"},{"time":40449,"text":"and to maybe be a little thin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42682,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":43800,"text":"Now, cavefishes can tell me\na lot about biology and geology."},{"time":48214,"text":"They can tell me how the landmasses\naround them have changed and moved"},{"time":52221,"text":"by being stuck in these little holes,"},{"time":54463,"text":"and they can tell me about\nthe evolution of sight, by being blind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":59193,"text":"Now, fish have eyes\nthat are essentially the same as ours."},{"time":62494,"text":"All vertebrates do, and each time\na fish species starts to adapt"},{"time":66346,"text":"to this dark, cold, cave environment,"},{"time":68782,"text":"over many, many generations,\nthey lose their eyes and their eyesight"},{"time":72743,"text":"until the end up like an eyeless\ncavefish like this one here."},{"time":75917,"text":"Now, each cavefish species\nhas evolved in a slightly different way,"},{"time":79778,"text":"and each one has a unique geological\nand biological story to tell us,"},{"time":83874,"text":"and that's why it's so exciting\nwhen we find a new species."}]},{"cues":[{"time":87217,"text":"So this is a new species\nwe described, from southern Indiana."},{"time":91075,"text":"We named it Amblyopsis hoosieri,\nthe Hoosier cavefish."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94996,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":96081,"text":"Its closest relatives\nare cavefishes in Kentucky,"},{"time":99034,"text":"in the Mammoth Cave system."},{"time":100660,"text":"And they start to diverge\nwhen the Ohio River split them"},{"time":103717,"text":"a few million years ago."},{"time":105419,"text":"And in that time they developed\nthese subtle differences"},{"time":108186,"text":"in the genetic architecture\nbehind their blindness."},{"time":111289,"text":"There's this gene called rhodopsin\nthat's super-critical for sight."},{"time":114829,"text":"We have it, and these species have it too,"},{"time":117250,"text":"except one species has lost\nall function in that gene,"},{"time":120147,"text":"and the other one maintains it."},{"time":122234,"text":"So this sets up this beautiful\nnatural experiment"},{"time":126281,"text":"where we can look at the genes\nbehind our vision,"},{"time":129269,"text":"and at the very roots of how we can see."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133047,"text":"But the genes in these cavefishes"},{"time":134785,"text":"can also tell us\nabout deep geological time,"},{"time":137595,"text":"maybe no more so\nthan in this species here."},{"time":140079,"text":"This is a new species\nwe described from Madagascar"},{"time":142920,"text":"that we named Typhleotris mararybe."},{"time":146245,"text":"That means \"big sickness\" in Malagasy,"},{"time":149534,"text":"for how sick we got trying\nto collect this species."},{"time":152614,"text":"Now, believe it or not,"},{"time":154216,"text":"swimming around sinkholes\nfull of dead things"},{"time":156830,"text":"and cave full of bat poop"},{"time":158737,"text":"isn't the smartest thing you could\nbe doing with your life,"},{"time":161570,"text":"but YOLO."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163103,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":166922,"text":"Now, I love this species despite the fact\nthat it tried to kill us,"},{"time":171120,"text":"and that's because\nthis species in Madagascar,"},{"time":173939,"text":"its closest relatives\nare 6,000 kilometers away,"},{"time":176787,"text":"cavefishes in Australia."},{"time":178701,"text":"Now, there's no way a three-inch-long\nfreshwater cavefish"},{"time":182360,"text":"can swim across the Indian Ocean,"},{"time":184423,"text":"so what we found when we compared\nthe DNA of these species"},{"time":187278,"text":"is that they've been separated\nfor more than 100 million years,"},{"time":190599,"text":"or about the time that the southern\ncontinents were last together."},{"time":195875,"text":"So in fact, these species\ndidn't move at all."},{"time":198105,"text":"It's the continents that moved them."},{"time":199930,"text":"And so they give us, through their DNA,"},{"time":201977,"text":"this precise model and measure"},{"time":204422,"text":"of how to date and time\nthese ancient geological events."}]},{"cues":[{"time":209064,"text":"Now, this species here is so new"},{"time":211320,"text":"I'm not even allowed\nto tell you its name yet,"},{"time":213827,"text":"but I can tell you\nit's a new species from Mexico,"},{"time":216513,"text":"and it's probably already extinct."},{"time":218667,"text":"It's probably extinct because\nthe only known cave system it's from"},{"time":222038,"text":"was destroyed when a dam was built nearby."},{"time":224714,"text":"Unfortunately for cavefishes,"},{"time":226700,"text":"their groundwater habitat"},{"time":228304,"text":"is also our main source of drinking water."}]},{"cues":[{"time":231103,"text":"Now, we actually don't know\nthis species' closest relative, yet."},{"time":235825,"text":"It doesn't appear to be\nanything else in Mexico,"},{"time":238499,"text":"so maybe it's something in Cuba,"},{"time":240223,"text":"or Florida, or India."},{"time":242830,"text":"But whatever it is, it might tell us\nsomething new about the geology"},{"time":247359,"text":"of the Caribbean, or the biology\nof how to better diagnose"},{"time":250591,"text":"certain types of blindness."},{"time":252736,"text":"But I hope we discover this species\nbefore it goes extinct too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":256733,"text":"And I'm going to spend my one life"},{"time":258672,"text":"as an ichthyologist\ntrying to discover and save"},{"time":262233,"text":"these humble little blind cavefishes"},{"time":264827,"text":"that can tell us so much\nabout the geology of the planet"},{"time":268317,"text":"and the biology of how we see."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270672,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":271847,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}